dependency:
  $ mkpkg foo <<EOF
  > depends: [
  >   "foo-linux" {os = "linux"}
  >   "foo-macos" {os = "macos"}
  >   "foo-macos-test-only" {os = "macos" & with-test}
  > ]
  > EOF
  $ mkpkg foo-linux <<EOF
  > available: os = "linux"
  > EOF
  $ mkpkg foo-linux-test-only <<EOF
  > available: os = "linux"
  > EOF
  $ mkpkg foo-macos <<EOF
  > available: os = "macos"
  > EOF

With no "os" variable set in the workspace, none of the os-specific
